{"tid":2311033,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋對上一次真係覺得好開心係幾時","createTime":"2020-12-03T17:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T16:41:03.000Z","uid":115522,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c0cfdb4e52e2b87a4315886a48f939d9be0b8448","tid":2311033,"uid":115522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"唔係話日日都會崩潰度日，偶然同啲朋友聚下 去下郊外 果刻係開心<br />\n<br />\n但某個時期開始就冇真係覺得好開心過<br />\n特別係每日都有新消息令你難過<br />\n又覺得呢啲無謂嘅感傷算係啲咩 如此無用<br />\n唯一令自己覺得幸福嘅事係同屋企人食飯 亦都好感恩<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日接收咗咁多壞消息 好難過但無從發洩<br />\n諗咗好耐 上一次覺得好開心係幾時呢<br />\n原來已經係好耐之前 喺堅尼地城海傍同好朋友睇日落 開心嘅事 始終離不開香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4457189ebb0b50517490c878686896762873a5cb","tid":2311033,"uid":190811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T17:17:05.000Z","msg":"聽到asus話11月會有多啲卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e890701ea067ee4c7f537ee8633e6e4769274779","tid":2311033,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62c4787b03d7e354bdcf84098ba1f0a726e6e0c7","tid":2311033,"uid":224843,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T17:18:12.000Z","msg":"分左手到宜家仲未開心過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ca99db23dad5d148bc5115689296261da17ff7","tid":2311033,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T17:18:44.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到人開po話分手果陣"},{"pid":"f336b6fe4b29e5fadf051489fd911c333dab47fd","tid":2311033,"uid":152403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T17:31:24.000Z","msg":"佢同我求婚"},{"pid":"6b0bc8f428886d9a287ef50d0fbd6c752b71f693","tid":2311033,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"佢拖我手仔"},{"pid":"43dc3a63e82f459a1a4348fc93ded060a79c6df2","tid":2311033,"uid":206834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited